data.description: Builder offering $5,000 towards closing costs when you contract in July! FLINTROCK BUILDERS sweeps AWARD after AWARD from The Parade of Homes YEAR after YEAR. Come out and see why! With amazing designs, decor, and a one-of-a-kind vision of ELEGANCE and GLAMOUR, this UNIQUE home is located in the newly opened phase of Heartwood Park in Copperas Cove! This GORGEOUS home will feature 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1564 sqft. It will offer an AMAZING OPEN FLOOR PLAN. The kitchen is going to have AWESOME features including, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, GRANITE COUNTERTOPS, and a PANTRY. There will be beautiful polished and sealed concrete floors throughout the home. All of the bedrooms will be SPACIOUS making the home feel much bigger than 1564 sq ft. The master bathroom will have GRANITE COUNTERTOPS, WALK IN SHOWER, and HIS & HER SINKS. The backyard will contain a COVERED PATIO for hanging out anytime of the year! This home offers a great floor plan for everyday living. The OPPORTUNITIES ARE ENDLESS!
